sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineProvider as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant RemoteProvider as RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>(in-process)
    participant DatasetIO as Llama Stack DatasetIO<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Llama Stack Inference<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ollama as Ollama/vLLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod<br/>(Kubernetes)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Ollama: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation
        Client->>LlamaStack: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack->>InlineProvider: dispatch eval request
        InlineProvider->>DatasetIO: get_rows_paginated()<br/>Python API (in-process)
        DatasetIO-->>InlineProvider: dataset rows
        InlineProvider->>Inference: chat_completion()<br/>Python API (in-process)
        Inference->>Ollama: POST /api/chat<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Ollama-->>Inference: LLM completion
        Inference-->>InlineProvider: completion result
        InlineProvider->>Inference: embeddings()<br/>Python API (in-process)
        Inference->>Ollama: POST /api/embeddings<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Ollama-->>Inference: embedding vectors
        Inference-->>InlineProvider: embedding result
        Note over InlineProvider: Ragas evaluate()<br/>answer_relevancy, context_precision,<br/>faithfulness, context_recall
        InlineProvider-->>LlamaStack: evaluation scores + generations
        LlamaStack-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LlamaStack: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack->>RemoteProvider: dispatch eval request

        RemoteProvider->>K8sAPI: GET ConfigMap<br/>trustyai-service-operator-config<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>RemoteProvider: ragas-provider-image

        RemoteProvider->>KFP: POST /healthz<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteProvider: healthy

        RemoteProvider->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func()<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteProvider: run_id

        RemoteProvider-->>LlamaStack: job_id (KFP run_id)
        LlamaStack-->>Client: job submitted response

        Note over KFPPod: KFP Pipeline Execution
        KFP->>KFPPod: schedule pipeline pods

        KFPPod->>LlamaStack: Step 1: retrieve_data<br/>GET datasets<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack-->>KFPPod: dataset rows

        KFPPod->>LlamaStack: Step 2: run_ragas<br/>POST completions + embeddings<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack->>Ollama: inference requests<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Ollama-->>LlamaStack: inference responses
        LlamaStack-->>KFPPod: inference results

        Note over KFPPod: Ragas evaluate()
        KFPPod->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFPPod: stored

        Client->>LlamaStack: GET /alpha/eval/job/status<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack->>RemoteProvider: check status
        RemoteProvider->>KFP: get_run()<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteProvider: run status
        RemoteProvider-->>LlamaStack: status
        LlamaStack-->>Client: job status

        Client->>LlamaStack: GET /alpha/eval/job/result<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LlamaStack->>RemoteProvider: get results
        RemoteProvider->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM (s3fs)
        S3-->>RemoteProvider: evaluation results
        RemoteProvider-->>LlamaStack: scores + generations
        LlamaStack-->>Client: JSON response
    end
